<PageLayout 
  title="About Us | TokenCalc AI" 
  description="Learn more about TokenCalc AI and our mission to provide developers with accurate AI API cost estimations."
>
  <h1>About TokenCalc AI</h1>
  
  <p>Welcome to <strong>TokenCalc AI</strong>. We are a dedicated team of developers and AI enthusiasts who understand the challenges of building scalable applications with Large Language Models (LLMs).</p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>Our mission is simple: to make AI development more transparent, predictable, and cost-effective. As API usage scales, unpredictable billing can quickly become a bottleneck for innovation. We built TokenCalc AI to provide developers, researchers, and startups with the exact tools they need to forecast and manage their inference costs.</p>

  <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
  <p>While testing various prompts and models across OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google, we noticed a recurring problem: it was extremely difficult to estimate the financial impact of deploying an AI feature at scale without actually running the code and waiting for the invoice.</p>
  
  <p>TokenCalc AI solves this by bringing precise, token-level cost calculation directly into the browser. By leveraging algorithms like <code>tiktoken</code>, we provide 100% client-side, zero-latency estimations.</p>

  <h2>Open Source & Privacy First</h2>
  <p>We believe in transparency. That's why our calculator operates entirely within your browser. Your prompts are never sent to our servers, ensuring your sensitive data and proprietary logic remain completely private.</p>

  <p>Thank you for using our tool. We are constantly updating our database with the latest model pricing to ensure you always have the most accurate estimations available.</p>

</PageLayout>
